{"tid":673270,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"望遠不如你執柒咗kaiboard佢啦","createTime":"2018-05-21T16:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T01:51:53.000Z","uid":3072,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6755358c3e0105f3c9ea29fb67b28967438860","tid":673270,"uid":3072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"多bug到仆街<br />\n<br />\n上次更新已經5個月前<br />\n十問九唔應<br />\n<br />\n話會跟進，跟到5個月得今日都仲食緊屎<br />\n<br />\n你每日用個咁嘅keyboard都仲咁忍得手真係唔撚話得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：乜春dlc都買齊"},{"pid":"3c598bbd121b43240be7168e72236d7ce183fdbe","tid":673270,"uid":3072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多bug到仆街<br />\n<br />\n上次更新已經5個月前<br />\n十問九唔應<br />\n<br />\n話會跟進，跟到5個月<del>得</del><span style=\"color: red;\">到</span>今日都仲食緊屎<br />\n<br />\n你每日用個咁嘅keyboard都仲咁忍得手真係唔撚話得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：乜春dlc都買齊</blockquote><br />\n炆到字都打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d018596ddf5c4bac6b1c424395aeb846b81b67b5","tid":673270,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34b4fbca898dc93f4df02bbd75c91ef8e86757d","tid":673270,"uid":3,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"其實都回應過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/611216/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/611216/2</a><br />\n#40<br />\n我再講詳細啲啦<br />\n<br />\n睇返 log 現時 9 成 crash 都係嚟自 system 本身<br />\n其中主要來自 iOS PluginKit 係未 load 到 keyboard 之前已經自己 crash 左，我根本控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n係好耐之前 iOS 版本已經係咁，到依家都未 fix，可以睇返其他 custom keyboard 嘅 developer 嘅問題：<br />\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/32736214/ios-keyboard-extension-crash-before-any-of-my-code-runs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F32736214%2Fios-keyboard-extension-crash-before-any-of-my-code-runs&d=yXH8c9SOQ%2F4fUYvQLvxUUACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5d38fc4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/32736214/ios-keyboard-extension-crash-before-any-of-my-code-runs</a><br />\n<br />\n另外發現到一個系統導致嘅爆 ram 問題<br />\ncustom keyboard ram limit 係 40mb<br />\n<br />\n個情況係咁<br />\n例如第一次開 keyboard 用左 25mb ram<br />\n第二次開嗰陣，如果 system 未 release 哂第一次啲 ram 已經 load 咗，加埋超過 40mb 都會即 crash<br />\n我用過嘅所有 custom key 都有以上問題，巴打可以試下<br />\n<br />\nKaiboard 輸入法 index table 嘅 ram usage 唔多，已經用左 mmap 去盡量避免將大量 data 放入 ram 到 process<br />\n主要 ram usage 係來自 ui，我要做嘅唯有將成個 keyboard ui cache 變成一整張圖，然後手動計返每次 touch 嘅 position 係對返張圖邊粒掣，要重寫大部份嘅 code，而且改善效果唔見得十分顯著，同埋會大幅減低日後開發嘅效率<br />\n<br />\n根本 Apple 就唔想繼續發展 custom keyboard<br />\n到依家仲未 support audio dictation / siri, bluetooth / extend keyboard, lock screen 又唔可以用<br />\n佢個 PluginKit 亦都好耐無 optimize 過<br />\n<br />\n我都想 crash 少啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38d68bd9ef68f23e811debdfc8bd0239e4dffb6","tid":673270,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d273baddaf2678b03fd4a339e776d7f7d426bd7a","tid":673270,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T18:46:05.000Z","msg":"出an版得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769c820058218c9d5a8dd9a85c41690e71866eae","tid":673270,"uid":3072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e34b4fbca898dc93f4df02bbd75c91ef8e86757d","tid":673270,"uid":3,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"其實都回應過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/611216/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/611216/2</a><br />\n#40<br />\n我再講詳細啲啦<br />\n<br />\n睇返 log 現時 9 成 crash 都係嚟自 system 本身<br />\n其中主要來自 iOS PluginKit 係未 load 到 keyboard 之前已經自己 crash 左，我根本控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n係好耐之前 iOS 版本已經係咁，到依家都未 fix